    "Enjoy your newly repaired shirt!",
    "Gather the necessary materials: You will need a shirt, thread, a needle, and a button.",
    "If your shirt has a buttonhole, you can use that; otherwise, you'll have to create one using a buttonhole template or a pattern. 2.",
    "Mark the location of the buttonhole: Use a marker or chalk to mark the location where you want to place the buttonhole.",
    "This should be centered on the front of the shirt, just below the collar. 3."
